  npcName: Old Man
  npcPortait: {fileID: -7527145504033472756, guid: 524df65bf2cd3a64396fc2bd3fcd1b75, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Hello, young one.
  - Beyond that gate lies the desert... and beyond that, endelss waves of the dead.
  - You seem brave. But do not underestimate them.
  - Not even I could stand against them, back in my day.
  - If you truly wish to face them, go... but fight smart, not just hard. Every wave
    will test you more then the last
  - ... May the gate remember you when you return.
